{"id":362495,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":3}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"劳动者之歌","genre":"","count":"215","ytitle":"","mtitle":"钢铁厂的黎明","ftitle":"","authors":["吴顺智"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原钢铁厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太原钢铁厂　吴顺智"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眨着眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍峨的鼓风炉像把大天梭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梭理着头上片片散云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水出炉射出亿万颗金星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮没了满天星星的眼睛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉吐火舌，轧钢机窜火龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片红光满天映。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载钢铁出厂的列车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像飞腾的长龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声怒吼冲开了东方的天口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先明朗起来的是无数参天的烟囱……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞姑娘出来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给满厂披上一身红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红纸喜报贴出来了:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜冶炼时间又缩短了三分钟!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场房红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁工人们的心更红!……"}]}